def_cn: 有特权的；享受特殊待遇的
def_en: Someone who is privileged has an advantage or opportunity that most other people do not have, often because of their wealth or high social class.

def_cn: （信息）保密的，只有少数人知道的
def_en: Privileged information is known by only a small group of people, who are not legally required to give it to anyone else.
